"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"DAOs are one of the most commented things out there and everyone’s trying to make one but just a few really know how.\\n\\nA DAO is a community and a way to empower people with the same interests so voting is the best mechanism on the blockchain to make it work, that’s why Snapshot exists.\\n\\n[Snapshot](https://snapshot.org) is an off-chain voting platform powered by [Ethereum signatures](https://medium.com/mycrypto/the-magic-of-digital-signatures-on-ethereum-98fe184dc9c7) turning transactions gasless on any chain and includes a hub full of different projects, called **spaces.**\\n\\n## First Steps\\n\\nIn order to create a great decentralized community, you must have some tools to offer to the people just like:\\n\\n* **Vault** - Where the community treasure lives. Used to fund building and payments over time. My suggestion is **[Gnosis Safe](https://gnosis-safe.io/)**\\n* **Govern** - May be an on-chain govern like **[Compound’s Bravo](https://compound.finance/governance)** or a **Snapshot space**.\\n* **Membership** - Can be a fungible or non fungible token used to gate people to the **DAO** turning every holder into a member and granting voting power.\\n* **Communication** - **[Discord](https://discord.com/)** or **[Telegram](https://telegram.org/)**, the good old apps.\\n\\nSo in order to make your vault, head over to the [Gnosis Safe](https://gnosis-safe.io/) and follow the steps for the desired network.\",\"timestamp\":1640872318,\"title\":\"How to make an awesome DAO or upgrade yours to a next level\"},\"digest\":\"FmakAZ53VTw5sOjmZhMIpTCvtKS0cIIYYdiRdWsYwvg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9E5d22a7Be252c01Eebd4a4568e2D644ac1ee5c6\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"sUEg-uXQLAJ5ccWIyXUuJ70HnWTbRXrx46J8d-Sc1II\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"dr5p5J_p1k-_LcVfs9JnC1YXHWtV0uqC9qkQt7Ppeno\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Sr49xllkSNXVus5lTEmJ6bENv4NVJ5Jjpfh3y5